text: Nyang tem beulanja geubri napakah Geubri seudeukah hana geutimang g Bak watee seunang got watee susah C Ek geutheun ate ‘oh watee beungeh Geukhem teuseuheh han jadeh marah Lom geupeumeu‘ah keu manusia Allah Taʻala Neugaseh leupah Soe nyang pubuet got keu ureueng laen Ureueng nyan meucen geunaseh Allah
